@tag2
Scenario Outline: Title of your scenario outline
Given I want to write a step with <name>
When I check for the <value> in step
Then I verify the <status> in step

Examples:
    | name  |value | status |
    | name1 |  5   | success|
    | name2 |  7   | Fail   |
